Package: cmR
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of Cardiac Magnetic Resonance Images
Version: 0.3.25
Date: 2021-03-25
Author: Volker Schmid [aut, cre]
Authors@R: c(person("Volker", "Schmid", role = c("aut", "cre"),
		     email = "volker.schmid@lmu.de"))
Maintainer: Volker Schmid <volker.schmid@lmu.de>
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: Matrix, splines, fields, graphics, parallel
Description: Analysis of cardiac magnetic resonance images. Computes maximum response using spatial and voxel wise spline based Bayesian model. This is an implemenation of the methods described in Schmid (2011): Voxel-Based Adaptive Spatio-Temporal Modelling of Perfusion Cardiovascular MRI. IEEE TMI 30(7) p. 1305 - 1313.
License: GPL-3
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://bioimaginggroup.github.io/cmr/
Suggests: 
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    codetools,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    R.rsp
VignetteBuilder: knitr, R.rsp
BugReports: https://github.com/bioimaginggroup/cmR/issues
